      <p>This mathematical analysis is for educational and informational purposes only. It is not investment advice, a recommendation to buy or sell securities, or a solicitation of any kind. The intrinsic value estimate is based on derived calculations that may not fully encapsulate real-world risks.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
